  <description><![CDATA[<p>The striking Hotel Principi di Piemonte is in great ski-in/ski-out position to make the most of the slopes. Its eye catching design is continued inside with a clever mix of natural wood and stone decor, giving it a warm mountain lodge feel. Picture windows in the restaurant are a main feature and provide stunning views over the valley. It offers excellent facilities including elegant lounge with bar and restaurant. Smart wellness centre (pay locally) with pool, sauna, steam room and gym; beauty treatments and massages are also available. The hotel provides a free shuttle bus to the centre of Sestriere in the morning and in the afternoon. All rooms have bath, TV, hairdryer, minibar and safe. Superior rooms are more spacious with a mountain view. Single rooms have a shower.</p>]]></description>
